highlights.text: “Tiago PZK: Bzrp Music Sessions, Vol. 48” by Bizarrap and Tiago PZK is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #37.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Blinding Lights” is the highest at #17.
“Friday (feat. Mufasa & Hypeman) - Dopamine Re-Edit” by Riton, Nightcrawlers, Mufasa & Hypeman, and Dopamine is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 126 spots at #68.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 257 weeks straight.
